{
  "title": "SerializationRegistry",
  "description": "Bidirectional name ↔ constructor ↔ NodeSerializer registry backing the scene serializer. Serialize resolves a node to its serializer by walking the constructor's prototype chain (so a subclass without its own registration inherits the nearest registered base serializer); deserialize resolves by type name. Core registers the built-in node types; extensions contribute their own via the Extension.serializers binding.",
